imdb.plot outline: Ever wanted to know what really goes on in a Stripclub? Neon lights beckon you to step inside. A DJ Spins. The girls sway under the hot lights. But that's only half the Story. Your Half. The Dancers have their own desires. Their innermost secrets. Always hidden from view. Until Now. Tonight, all will be revealed as we go behind the scenes. An all access pass into the Dancers' wildest fantasies. Welcome to: Untold Stories: Strip Club Confessions.
